        players:'Goalkeepers: #21 Domagoj Mamic, #1 Teo Novak, #12 Josip Silic, #21 Tomislav Tomic, #1 Oliver Zelenika; Defenders: #30 Enes Alic, #5 Lamine Ba, #44 Mateo Barac, #25 Antonio Borsic, #3 Vane Jovanov, #23 Frane Maglica, #13 Mario Mladenovski, #4 Luka Skaricic, #16 Novak Tepsic; Midfielders: #14 Ante Coric, #17 Mario Cuic, #8 Tomislav Duvnjak, #24 Mario Marina, #7 Jurica Poldrugac, #18 Vito Segovic, #14 Jaime Sierra Mateos; Forwards: #11 Mate Antunovic, #9 Marko Dabro, #27 Aleksa Latkovic, #22 Luka Mamic, #26 Atdhe Mazari, #17 Dimitar Mitrovski, #19 Thierry Nevers, #15 Matej Vuk; Coach: Nikola Safaric',
